tiers.ability_description:
At the start of battle, Jawa allies gain 100% bonus Protection until the end of the encounter and all enemies are inflicted with Provoked for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever a Jawa ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Jawa allies gain Foresight for 1 turn. Whenever an enemy is inflicted with Thermal Detonators, Jawa allies gain 10% Defense and Offense (stacking, max 300%). At the start of each turn, if a Jawa ally has 50% or less Health, damage they receive is reduced by 75% (excluding percent health damage and massive damage) until the end of the turn.

Whenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, which can't be evaded, Jawa allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and that enemy is inflicted with an aditional Thermal Detonator for 1 turn, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.

If all allies are First Order at the start of battle, First Order allies gain Damage Immunity for 2 turns. Whenever a First Order ally is critically hit, all First Order allies gain 10% Critical Damage (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter. Whenever a First Order ally attacks out of turn, all First Order allies gain 10% Offense (stacking, max 50%) until the end of the encounter.

First Order SF TIE Pilot has +100% Potency. While allied Supreme Leader Kylo Ren is active, First Order SF TIE Pilot can't be defeated. While First Order allies have Advantage, they ignore Taunt.

Whenever the ally in the Leader slot or First Order SF TIE Pilot is damaged while they have Advantage, Stun that enemy for 1 turn, which can't be resisted. Whenever an enemy is Stunned, First Order SF TIE Pilot's abilities gain 5% bonus damage (stacking, max 200%), he and the ally in the Leader slot gain 10% Max Health until the end of the encounter, and if the ally in the Leader slot is Supreme Leader Kylo Ren, he gains 5% Ultimate Charge. Whenever a Stunned enemy is defeated, they can't be revived, the ally in the Leader slot gains a bonus turn, and the allied Leader and First Order SF TIE Pilot recover 100% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

At the start of each encounter, grant all allies Evasion Up and Tenacity Up for 2 turns and inflict Tenacity Down and Evasion Down on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a non-support ally is critically hit, grant them Protection Up (20%, stacking, max 100%) for 2 turns.

At the start of their turn, Support allies dispel all buffs on all enemies. If Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, Potency Up, or Tenacity Up were dispelled, inflict the opposite debuff on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever a Support is critically hit or inflicted with a debuff, they Stealth for 1 turn.
